汹，大部地区降温剧烈，且风力较大，公众需及时增添衣物，做好保暖措施，关注人体健康，外出时需远离临时搭建物，防范高空坠物。此外，公众还需防范雨雪天气对交通出行的不利影响，尤其是北方地区公众需防范雨雪及道路积雪、结冰、低能见度、路面湿滑等的不利影响。中央气象台：今年入冬以来最强寒潮来袭，中东部大部地区气温暴跌 | 界面新闻 · 快讯"}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "59 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/568600794"}}, "attached_info": "ClQIwvzY2ueog8QyEAMaCDg4NjM4MDg5IM7T/JsGMAE4QUAncgk1Njg2MDA3OTR4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAPIBEwgBEg9kb21haW5fb3BlcmF0b3I="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "40_1669327681.938879", "card_id": "Q_568342192", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 35}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何看待 80 后女生辞职看世界杯？你会为了热爱的事情放弃工作吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "上海 80 后女子乔西辞职去看世界杯引发热议，有人觉得「30 多岁辞职去看世界杯并不理智」。 你会为了热爱的事情放弃工作吗？80 后女生辞职看世界杯引热议，当事人回应"}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "59 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/568342192"}}, "attached_info": "ClQIwvzY2ueog8QyEAMaCDg4NTgwNjQyIOf39ZsGMAU4NEAocgk1NjgzNDIxOTJ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAPIBEwgBEg9kb21haW5fb3BlcmF0b3I="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "41_1669327681.9394908", "card_id": "Q_22996751", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 4629}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "人不自信的最根本原因是什么？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "关于人不自信这个问题，已经有很多回答了，但是几乎都很粗糙，没有真正的体现出本质，我希望能了解其本质，并从根本上来改善 & 克服这个问题"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-6279e196c3f89fc1c76af0a0998d9ea3_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "59 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/22996751"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4IwvzY2ueog8QyEAMaBzEzNzk1ODE